    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
  - logical "xor"
 </p>
 <p>Matrix multiplication</p>
 <p>
