 </p>
 <h4>Matrix-scalar</h4>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>A</var>
   </b>
   =
   <span class="b0">[</span>
   0; 1; 2
   <span class="b0">|</span>
   3; 4; 5
   <span class="b0">]</span>
   =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
     <span class="td">2</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">3</span>
     <span class="td">4</span>
     <span class="td">5</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>b</var>
   = 2
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>Arithmetic:</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>A</var>
   </b>
   <sup>
    <small class="nth">⊙</small>
    2
   </sup>
   =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
     <span class="td">4</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">9</span>
     <span class="td">16</span>
     <span class="td">25</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
  - exponentiation
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <span class="dvc">
    <b>
     <var>A</var>
    </b>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">0.5</span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">1.5</span>
     <span class="td">2</span>
     <span class="td">2.5</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
  - floating point division
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>A</var>
   </b>
   \2 =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
     <span class="td">2</span>
     <span class="td">2</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
  - integer division
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>A</var>
   </b>
   <em>/</em>
   2 =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">0.5</span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
